title: Lol won an rp giveaway and didn't even know.
body:
I entered an RP giveaway back at the start of July and apparently I won and I only just checked my twitter today. RIP.

http://imgur.com/a/YAadk

Someone else could have got the money but my retarded self got it instead.

replies.body: Can you still get what you have won?
Probs not they have a timed expiration on stuff like this.
